{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/ec-07122023073011.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-07-12T11:06:00-04:00", "modified time": "2023-07-12T13:02:43-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "\u9999\u6e2f\u8b66\u65b9\u6548\u6cd5\u4e2d\u56fd\u5185\u5730\u3000\u5bf9\u88ab\u901a\u7f09\u8005\u5b9e\u65bd\u8fde\u5750", "description": "\u9999\u6e2f\u56fd\u5b89\u8b66\u5f15\u7528\u4e2d\u56fd\u9488\u5bf9\u5f02\u89c1\u4eba\u58eb\u5bb6\u5c5e\u65bd\u4ee5\u7684\u8fde\u5750\u60e9\u7f5a\uff0c\u5e26\u8d70\u88ab\u901a\u7f09\u7684\u7f57\u51a0\u806a\u5bb6\u4eba\u3002\u540c\u5728\u901a\u7f09\u540d\u5355\u4e0a\u7684\u8bb8\u667a\u5cf0\u6279\u8bc4\u6e2f\u8b66\u7684\u8fd9\u4e00\u505a\u6cd5\u5e76\u5f3a\u8c03\uff0c\u5a01\u80c1\u4e0d\u4f1a\u6709\u6210\u6548\u3002", "videos": [], "audios": ["https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/ec-07122023073011.html/@@stream"], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/ec-07122023073011.html/@@images/1521427e-da5b-4417-b3b4-516db5aea070.jpeg\"/>\n\u9999\u6e2f\u4eba\u884c\u5929\u6865\u4e0a\uff0c\u56fd\u65d7\u548c\u9999\u6e2f\u7279\u533a\u533a\u65d7\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/ec-07122023073011.html/@@images/image\">\n <img src=\"https://www.rfa.org//++plone++rfa-resources/img/icon-zoom.png\"/>\n</a>\n\u7f8e\u8054\u793e\u56fe\u7247\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n var audio_title = {\"audio_name\": \"\\u9999\\u6e2f\\u8b66\\u65b9\\u6548\\u6cd5\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u5185\\u5730\\u3000\\u5bf9\\u88ab\\u901a\\u7f09\\u8005\\u5b9e\\u65bd\\u8fde\\u5750\"};\n</script>\n<script>\n eventer = function(id){\n            var data = {\n                    \"tealium_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"on_page_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"audio_name\": audio_title['audio_name'],\n                    \"article_uid\": utag_data[\"art